<head>
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
  <!--모달 창-->
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/login/modal.css' />

  <link rel="preload" as="style" href="/stylesheets/header.css" onload="this.rel='stylesheet'">
  <!-- 웹폰트 1-->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jua&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- 웹폰트 2-->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sunflower:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <!--구글 아이콘-->
  <link rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@48,400,0,0" />

</head>

<body>
  <div id="load_div">
    <img src="/images/loading.gif" alt="loading">
  </div>
  <header id="content" style="display:none">
    <nav id="header_nav">
      <div style="width: auto;"><a href="/"><img src="images/logo_transparent.png" style="width:80%;"></a></div>
      <div class="scrollable-div">
        <div id="welcome-message"></div>
        <div class="scrolling-text">
          <%= notice %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="login_div">
        <button id="one" class="button"> <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="margin-left:10px;width: 30px;">
            login
          </span></button>
        <button id="logout"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="width: 30px;">
            logout
          </span></button>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <%- include ('./login/modal') %>

      <div class="slider">
        <div class="items-group">
          <div class="item">
            <h1 style="position:absolute;  right:20vw; text-align: center;">
              안녕하세요!<br><br>
              김도현의 포트폴리오 사이트입니다.</h1>
            <div class="block" style="position:absolute; left:10vw;">
              <span class="circleLight"></span>
              <div class="text">
                <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
                <p style="font-weight: 700; color:black"></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <h1 style="position:absolute;  right:10vw; text-align: center;">
              이 사이트는 <br><br>가로 1440px, 세로 810px 환경에 최적화되어 있습니다.</h1>
            <div class="block" style="position:absolute; left:10vw;">
              <span class="circleLight"></span>
              <div class="text">
                <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
                <p>해상도</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <h1 style="position:absolute;  right:10vw; text-align: center;">
              이 사이트는 <br><br>Node.js, MySQL, Express.js, HTML5, CSS, JavaScript <br><br>환경에서 구현되었습니다.<br><br>
              추후 새로운 언어를 공부할 때마다 추가할 계획입니다. </h1>
            <div class="block" style="position:absolute; left:10vw;">
              <span class="circleLight"></span>
              <div class="text">
                <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
                <p>개발환경</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <h1 style="position:absolute;  right:10vw; text-align: center;">
              궁금하신 게 있다면 <a href="/visitors_book?page=1" title="방명록">방명록</a>에 글을 남겨 주세요!</h1>
            <div class="block" style="position:absolute; left:10vw;">
              <span class="circleLight"></span>
              <div class="text">
                <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
                <p></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="navigations">
          <ul class="dots" style="border-style: none;"></ul>
          <span id="resize_header" class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 30px; margin:0 0 20px 20px; cursor:pointer;">
            unfold_more
          </span>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div id="short_header_div" class="navigations" style="margin-top:56px;width:100%; height: 56px; display:none;">
        <div id="resize_header_2nd" style="display:flex; height:100%; align-items:center; cursor:pointer;">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 30px; margin:0 20px 0 20px">
            unfold_more
          </span><span>CLICK HERE TO TOGGLE MAIN BANNER</span>
        </div>
      </div>
  </header>


</body>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.4.min.js"></script>
<script src="/javascripts/header.js"></script>

